\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
With this system, you're looking to improve your buy and sell points.
 For most growth investors, the price 3 months before the buy should be
 lower than the buy price.
 For value investors, the price three months before the buy should be higher
 than the buy price.
 Value investors expect to buy when stocks go on sale.
 With selling, everybody wants the same thing here - to sell at the top
 just before the stock dives to lower prices.
 Growth and value investors can agree on this point.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Look over several fearsome foursomes for different stocks you've owned.
 Watch for trends.
 If you're consistently buying or selling too soon or too late, make note
